ee, Except a man be born of water and of the Spirit, he cannot enter into the kingdom of God.","year":30},{"id":"recH5Q0KesC3E7khS","ref":"John.3.6","text":"That which is born of the flesh is flesh; and that which is born of the Spirit is spirit.","year":30},{"id":"receMWoWGWqHalih0","ref":"John.3.7","text":"Marvel not that I said unto thee, Ye must be born again.","year":30},{"id":"recxOPBT90HNVkcnD","ref":"John.3.8","text":"The wind bloweth where it listeth, and thou hearest the sound thereof, but canst not tell whence it cometh, and whither it goeth: so is every one that is born of the Spirit.","year":30}]}
